title: 1v1 Tournament Starting again next week

embed.description: This organization will run tournaments for teams and players of all ranks and skill level, with a main focus on League Of Legends in the Oceanic Region.

body:
Hi,

I just wanted to let people know that the 1v1 tournament that I run will be starting up again on thursday next week.

1000rp will be awarded to the winner, and all participants will receive a 4-win IP boost.

For more details follow the link https://battlefy.com/digital-puppet-masters
